==Finnish==
===Noun===

kulli (plural ''kullit'')

# ''(vulgar)'' cock, dick, prick, schlong (singular) [[penis]], (plural) male genitalia
# ''(ancient Finnish)'' penis

*Respective male word for ancient Finnish ''vittu'', female genitalia.

===Derived terms===

*(''vulgar, humorous'') ''kullinluikaus'', ''kullin luikaus'' a short trip or period of time. ''Meiltä on paikalliseen baariin vain kullinluikaus.'' It's just a short trip from our place to the local bar.

